      "raw_text": "A recommendation for a water\nmain on Fifth avenue, from d to E\nstreets, has been filed by the board\nof public works with the city clerk,\nto be submitted to the city council\nThe water mains will cost 1882 so,\naccording to an estimate, and the\nparties who signed the petition ask\ning for the same, show a revenue\nof $58."
